  "content": "{\n  \"cards\": [\n    {\n      \"front\": \"What is remote authentication?\",\n      \"back\": \"The process of verifying a user's identity without physically meeting the user, typically through digital means such as passwords, biometrics, or smart cards.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"front\": \"What is a one-time password (OTP)?\",\n      \"back\": \"A password that is valid for only a short period of time (usually a few minutes) and is used to verify a user's identity for a single login attempt.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"fron"
